<h1>Function Health review<br>&#8212; <em>the most complete panel available.</em></h1>
<p class="review-hero-sub">At $365/year with two annual draws and 160+ directly measured biomarkers, Function Health is the most comprehensive subscription-based testing service on the market. Here&#8217;s what you actually get, what it&#8217;s worth, and when Superpower or à la carte testing is the better call.</p>
</section>

