<div class="verdict-title">Verdict: Best comprehensive panel for active health management</div>
<p class="verdict-text">Function Health is the most thorough consumer biomarker service available at a non-concierge price point. Two annual draws, 160+ directly measured markers, cancer screening, heavy metals, and ANA autoimmune screen set it apart from every competitor. The twice-yearly cadence is the key differentiator &#8212; the ability to baseline, intervene, and retest within a single membership year is clinically meaningful. At $365/year, it&#8217;s the right choice for anyone actively managing cardiovascular, hormonal, or metabolic health. At $199/year, Superpower is the right entry point for everyone else.</p>
