<div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much does Function Health cost?</div>
<div class="faq-answer">$365/year as of 2026, reduced from the original $499 launch price. HSA/FSA eligible. A $25 discount is typically available via member referral link &#8212; referral links are the only reliable discount mechanism; promo codes circulating on coupon sites are generally expired or invalid.</div>
